@prefix : <http://example.com/> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

:Vegetarian a owl:Class ;
  rdfs:subClassOf [
    a owl:Restriction ;
    owl:onProperty :eats ;
    owl:allValuesFrom :Plant
  ] .

:Plant a owl:Class .
:eats a owl:ObjectProperty .
